            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8833,
            "LocalizeKR": "어머나, 별똥별이에요!\n앗… 저기도! 또 저기도!",
            "LocalizeJP": "うわっ、流れ星です！\nあっ……あそこにも！\nそっちにも！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 290,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8167,
            "LocalizeKR": "하늘에 별똥별이 가득해요!\n정말 유성이 비처럼 내리네요!",
            "LocalizeJP": "空に流れ星がいっぱいです！\n流星が本当に、\n雨のように降ってますね！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 300,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10500,
            "LocalizeKR": "이렇게 아름다운 광경을\n직접 눈으로 볼 수 있다니…\n정말 꿈만 같네요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "こんなに美しい光景を\n実際に見られるなんて……\n本当に、夢みたいです。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 310,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3500,
            "LocalizeKR": "소원이요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "願い事ですか？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 320,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7000,
            "LocalizeKR": "아니…\n오늘은 괜찮아요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "いえ……\n今日は、大丈夫です。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 330,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5500,
            "LocalizeKR": "좋아하는 사람과\n아름다운 광경을\n함께 지켜볼 수 있는데,",
            "LocalizeJP": "好きな人と一緒に、\nこんなに綺麗な星空を\n見ることができているのに、",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 340,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6500,
            "LocalizeKR": "여기서 더한 소원을 빌면\n어쩐지 별님에게\n혼이 날 것 같아서…",
            "LocalizeJP": "これ以上願い事をしたら、\nなんだかお星様に\n叱られてしまいそうで……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26006,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600601,
            "DisplayOrder": 350,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6833,
            "LocalizeKR": "오늘은 이것으로\n만족할래요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "今日はこれだけで、\n満足です。",
